"{\"value\":{\"mdx\":\"# Accounts and Subaccounts\\n\\nAccounts and subaccounts serve as identifiers in the dYdX ecosystem.\\n\\n## Main Account\\n\\nA (main) account is associated with a public-private keypair, and with a trader's on-chain identity.\\n\\n* Known publicly and associated with an address;\\n* Holds tokens/assets that are sent to/from the chain, including tokens used for gas and collateral;\\n* Gas for transactions is used from the main account;\\n* Main accounts cannot trade;\\n* Several main accounts can be derived from the same mnemonic phrase. Each user main account is completely independent and private/unlinkable from each other.\\n\\n## Subaccounts\\n\\nSubaccounts provide a way to isolate funds and manage risk within an account. They are used to trade.\\n\\n* Each main account can have 128,001 subaccounts;\\n* Each subaccount is uniquely identified using as subaccount ID of `(main account address, integer)`;\\n* Once you deposit funds to a valid subaccount ID, the subaccount will automatically be created;\\n* Only the main account can send transactions on behalf of a subaccount;\\n* Subaccounts do not require gas (no gas is used for trading);\\n* Subaccounts require collateral token (currently USDC) in order to trade.\\n\",\"document\":[{\"href\":\"/concepts/trading/accounts#accounts-and-subaccounts\",\"html\":\"</header>\\n<p>Accounts and subaccounts serve as identifiers in the dYdX ecosystem.</p>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/concepts/trading/accounts.mdx#accounts-and-subaccounts\",\"isPage\":true,\"text\":\"\\nAccounts and subaccounts serve as identifiers in the dYdX ecosystem.\\n\",\"title\":\"Accounts and Subaccounts\",\"titles\":[]},{\"href\":\"/concepts/trading/accounts#main-account\",\"html\":\"\\n<p>A (main) account is associated with a public-private keypair, and with a trader&#x27;s on-chain identity.</p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Known publicly and associated with an address;</li>\\n<li>Holds tokens/assets that are sent to/from the chain, including tokens used for gas and collateral;</li>\\n<li>Gas for transactions is used from the main account;</li>\\n<li>Main accounts cannot trade;</li>\\n<li>Several main accounts can be derived from the same mnemonic phrase. Each user main account is completely independent and private/unlinkable from each other.</li>\\n</ul>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/concepts/trading/accounts.mdx#main-account\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\nA (main) account is associated with a public-private keypair, and with a trader&#x27;s on-chain identity.\\n\\nKnown publicly and associated with an address;\\nHolds tokens/assets that are sent to/from the chain, including tokens used for gas and collateral;\\nGas for transactions is used from the main account;\\nMain accounts cannot trade;\\nSeveral main accounts can be derived from the same mnemonic phrase. Each user main account is completely independent and private/unlinkable from each other.\\n\\n\",\"title\":\"Main Account\",\"titles\":[\"Accounts and Subaccounts\"]},{\"href\":\"/concepts/trading/accounts#subaccounts\",\"html\":\"\\n<p>Subaccounts provide a way to isolate funds and manage risk within an account. They are used to trade.</p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Each main account can have 128,001 subaccounts;</li>\\n<li>Each subaccount is uniquely identified using as subaccount ID of <code>(main account address, integer)</code>;</li>\\n<li>Once you deposit funds to a valid subaccount ID, the subaccount will automatically be created;</li>\\n<li>Only the main account can send transactions on behalf of a subaccount;</li>\\n<li>Subaccounts do not require gas (no gas is used for trading);</li>\\n<li>Subaccounts require collateral token (currently USDC) in order to trade.</li>\\n</ul>\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/concepts/trading/accounts.mdx#subaccounts\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\nSubaccounts provide a way to isolate funds and manage risk within an account. They are used to trade.\\n\\nEach main account can have 128,001 subaccounts;\\nEach subaccount is uniquely identified using as subaccount ID of (main account address, integer);\\nOnce you deposit funds to a valid subaccount ID, the subaccount will automatically be created;\\nOnly the main account can send transactions on behalf of a subaccount;\\nSubaccounts do not require gas (no gas is used for trading);\\nSubaccounts require collateral token (currently USDC) in order to trade.\\n\",\"title\":\"Subaccounts\",\"titles\":[\"Accounts and Subaccounts\"]}]}}"
